- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The optimization of initial solutions obtained by a course grid search involves AI techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper mentions the use of variable-resolution data received from probabilistic sensors, which may involve machine learning techniques for processing and analyzing the data.
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper mentions the real-time application on a photorealistic mapping scenario, which involves graphics techniques for rendering the terrain.
